{"tid":1126862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇法律撚講解一下法官判決背後嘅原理","createTime":"2019-04-26T16:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T12:20:06.000Z","uid":193485,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e3aa101f9e09a22e4906ca198a664a5e41e42cde","tid":1126862,"uid":193485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:15:04.000Z","msg":"點解最近睇既新聞，法官判決都好似咁撚on9<br />\n感覺上根本唔可以彰顯公義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似公屋富戶條友過千萬資產呃公屋住，淨係判社會服務令，但呃學資處grant loan就要坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然兩者都係呃，但點睇都過千萬資產仲呃公屋過份啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿婆因為𨋢公司同維修人員懶到仆街鳩做維修保養，俾lift夾死，佢地就淨係罰幾皮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仆你個街，人命嚟架wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁嚴重既人為事故，都唔要嚴懲殺一儆百？<br />\n<br />\n其實法官咁樣判係有冇根據？<br />\n定純粹真係個人觀感？<br />\n<br />\n定還是真係法律面前窮人含撚？"},{"pid":"6205e5c8bbc0af0667348a831f27981c0fa4dee4","tid":1126862,"uid":162095,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:17:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">定還是真係法律面前窮人含撚？</span><br />\n<br />\nYes"},{"pid":"d10a1e3051c26973c6b243939b940c215afa0000","tid":1126862,"uid":193485,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:19:06.000Z","msg":"呀，仲見到有巴打話個23歲仔攞錢兇鳩個曾經侮辱佢既阿蛇，最後判刑仲嚴重過阿婆俾𨋢夾死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0a1d26e71e18fe44769a79f3f59fe8aff2c87e","tid":1126862,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:21:22.000Z","msg":"喺香港，基本上真係有料嘅都唔會甘於去做普通官<br />\n即係判案嗰班其實係...你明啦"},{"pid":"f2c20a1a903789124067f7b57c46b0b87a90b1ca","tid":1126862,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:22:45.000Z","msg":"每天都發生呢D判決既<br />\n